Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:10.94,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:37.54,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, we're family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:38.87,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.81,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't share the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.14,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:46.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But we're more connected than\Npeople who share the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.15,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:49.90,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.98,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any blood relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.37,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but all of the friends we've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.45,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And all the friends we're going to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:06.87,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's treat them just like they're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:09.36,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there. Once we\Nget through this tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:32.14,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:35.15,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to dungeons?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.24,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how you get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the Black Bulls aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:46.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. There's no way they'd beat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.83,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.88,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:57.55,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,She's an expert at sensing mana,\Nbut she didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:02.04,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a trap spell... \NWhat is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.68,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:10.52,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Who stands in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.70,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:18.32,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Friends you can trust are \Nworth their weight in gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:23.13,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but stay there a while and get weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:28.05,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.33,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.34,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Keep winning, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.39,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.45,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.78,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,since things actually got interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,More... More!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.95,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:11.25,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not pluck a bud \Nthat's still so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:32.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:41.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:46.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.52,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:55.04,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:04:00.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:04.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.76,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:13.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:19.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:22.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.53,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.89,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.10,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you do something so simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.81,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.04,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.16,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you cry or get angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:06.74,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you born that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.93,flashback,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.40,flashback,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:38.35,flashback,Teacher A,0000,0000,0000,,One of the common students defeated a noble...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.69,flashback,Teacher B,0000,0000,0000,,That's never happened before in our \Nschool's magic exchange competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.93,flashback,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,It's not normal for a \Ncommoner to beat a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:49.81,flashback,Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I was picking on him. \NHe might try to get me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.55,flashback,Student C,0000,0000,0000,,He's always smiling... He's super creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.25,flashback,Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with him. \NHe'll beat you to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.71,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,You won against a noble using magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.17,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.47,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you had such powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.99,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, no one can beat a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.37,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,You must be special!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.97,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Keep winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:21.58,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win, win, and keep on \Nwinning with your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:24.05,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,No one will help you in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.49,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,You must use your own powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:33.75,flashback,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,If that will make you happy, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.40,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.95,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,So dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:47.67,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You've become faster and sharper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.52,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.41,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.51,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,With my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:01.27,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't afford to lose, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:07.32,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Creation Magic: Binding Cross Prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.20,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Solid smoke? I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:24.70,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,This uses up a lot of magic,\Nso I really didn't want to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.46,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:30.22,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to zip around anymore, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:34.63,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I wonder how our kid is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.85,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Ouchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:41.25,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He's not very good at communicating...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.98,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's the generation gap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.99,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Recovery Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.28,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Dream-Healing Flower Cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:11.17,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry... I'm supposed to be \Nthe healer, and I went down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:15.93,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about unnecessary things.\NRight now, concentrate on healing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:24.93,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That crest... Is he one of the invading\Nmages from the Diamond Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You dare attack someone from behind? \NIs that something a warrior should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.28,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.53,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.69,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're all the same.\NJust pebbles by the wayside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:53.13,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Back me up, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.04,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:59.14,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You Diamond scum! I'll show you the \Ntrue power of Clover's Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:02.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This path is a cinch to go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.46,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is getting denser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:11.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Is the treasure chamber really this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:21.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This magic is probably Luck's. \NI think he's fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that means the \Nenemy really did invade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy? We have to go help him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.84,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's better to just \Nleave the fighting to Luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:40.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemy really got in, I'm sure \Nthey're after the treasure chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It might be better to head over there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:49.56,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We need to take care of this mission fast \Nso Diamond's people won't steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:52.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the Golden Dawn \Nwill get ahead of us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:13.09,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Win... I have to keep \Nwinning with my powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:19.30,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there's something tying you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.81,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What I want... is going away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:30.81,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was the thing I wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:47.04,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's using such powerful \Nattacks without a grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:51.04,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, it doesn't appear \Nthat he's losing any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.29,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:58.76,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! You head to the treasure \Nchamber while I'm fighting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.51,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong. If you fight him \Nwithout support, even you won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:09.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I'd rather not leave \Nthis to a peasant like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.48,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But it's for our kingdom! Fulfill our duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.82,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.75,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set you free...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.80,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, we're family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.56,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But we're more connected than\Npeople who share the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:54.71,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've got another lively one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.57,flashbackitalics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.56,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.28,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.78,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.89,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any blood relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.46,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but all of the friends we've made...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.33,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You should be concentrating on the mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.50,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And all the friends we're going to make...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.06,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's treat them just like they're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.51,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.35,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...his friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.35,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:47.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! You head to the treasure \Nchamber while I'm fighting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.37,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:12.47,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set you free...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.69,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hurry up and \Nget to the treasure chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.96,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.14,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's defeat him and go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.24,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,All three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna have to face us, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:07.69,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... Having your friends show \Nup is definitely not in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:12.31,flashback,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she just suddenly dropped dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.21,flashback,Villager B,0000,0000,0000,,She always seemed to be \Nunder a lot of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:18.33,flashback,Villager C,0000,0000,0000,,And now her kid's all alone... How awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:22.13,flashback,Villager B,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not so sure. \NHer kid's sort of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.84,flashback,Villager A,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that his mother just died...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.09,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,He's my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.26,flashbackitalics,Luck's mother,0000,0000,0000,,Win...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.73,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win and keep offering \Nthose victories to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.61,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:51.24,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any friends. Just my powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.58,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Mom won't accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:05.42,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I shouldn't be holding back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:11.84,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.53,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,make Mom accept me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.02,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll be all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:31.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want! \NAnd I'll do what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.74,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave you alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.13,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Some part of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you think about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:56.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.24,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...was trying not to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:07.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've already acknowledged \Nyou as my... as our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:14.17,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...that I had friends I could rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:27.32,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mom. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.79,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:46.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,True, it seems like it'd be more \Nfun if we all fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:47.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.69,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.36,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make an old man get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:13.08,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Creation Magic: \NPrison of the Fallen King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.41,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to get away anymore, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who we're facing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:24.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,we, the Black Bulls, will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.44,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:42.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Creation Magic: Swift White Hawk\Nand Wind Blade Shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.46,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Simultaneous spell activation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.96,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And this power... H-He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:57.09,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It will be the Golden Dawn that \Nreaches the treasure chamber first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:12.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I cut and cut, but there's \Nno end! It keeps coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.99,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke just keeps getting thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.34,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're going to suffocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.72,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. We have to \Nhurry up and defeat that mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:47.05,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty much tell \Nwhere he is with my magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.89,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,but he'll probably dodge, even if I attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:53.98,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on our battle so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.93,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,he's able to travel at high \Nspeed within the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.41,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And his ability to sense magic is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:05.54,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,If we're to land a hit on him,\Nwe'll have to surprise him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.37,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we do that without \Nhim noticing our magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:18.05,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,The downside of this magic is \Nthat it drains my powers a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.36,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,My magic level is still fine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.30,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that and the fact that\NI can't see the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.60,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.18,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can sense your magic just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.90,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:45.53,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a barrage. Are you getting desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:51.08,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to hit me \Nor get rid of the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.71,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You're just wasting magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.70,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I think the difference in our \Nexperience levels is starting to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.21,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've fought far\Nmore mages than you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.72,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.15,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I chased him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:21.57,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And I suppressed my magic so \Nhe wouldn't notice, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.43,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:30.50,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He can't sense Asta, so Asta attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.55,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:38.28,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I guess teamwork really is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.26,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:24.73,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Begone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:49.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:59.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:05.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:07.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:10.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:13.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:21.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:24.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:26.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:35.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:41.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:44.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
