Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.33,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:03.77,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Family
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.04,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:05.60,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:10.03,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,So you decided that you would treat all of \Nthe friends you encountered like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.18,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,That's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:18.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Family... So basically, it's like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:25.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:28.53,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Little Brother, allow me \Nto bestow these upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:33.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:36.82,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.10,main,yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:47.23,main,yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm going to become the Wizard King,\N I can't be defeated here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:50.53,main,yuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 17: "Destroyer."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:55.25,sign_34249_284_Page_17__Destroy,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 17\N\N{\fs18}Destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:53.70,main,yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic.
